    "123060026": {
      "title": "On sharply n-transitive superstable groups",
      "abstract": "Abstract We study sharply n -transitive superstable groups for n = 2, 3. For n = 3 we get a complete classification, and for n = 2 we prove that such groups split if we also assume the surjectivity principle. These results generalize the algebraic case."
